divs: Sighting DetailsI was sitting in my back yard filming with my Sony IR camera. Took a minute to view the sky with my eye's instead of through the view finder and noticed n object in the sky, switched camera to normal mode and filmed for about 13 seconds until the disc shape disapperaed. About 5-7 minutes prior to filming the disc, I had to circular objects pass over my house that showed up on my video in IR mode however I was able to see them with the naked eye, only the camera was able to pick them up. I have several other videos of UFO's, just learning how to edit my footage.
